{{Quote|But it wasn't 'til Nar Shaddaa that we really started clickin'.''"<br />"''Right&hellip;those smugglers tried to jump you at the Slag Pit.''"<br />"''I had it handled, but no! One-a the roughest cantinas in the galaxy and this one gets us kicked out for fighting.|Greez Dritus and Cere Junda|<ref name="JFO" />}}
The '''Slag Pit''' was a [[cantina]] located on<ref name="JFO" /> the [[Outer Rim Territories]]<ref name="Star Wars 8">[[Star Wars (2015) 8|''Star Wars'' (2015) 8]]</ref> [[moon]] [[Nar Shaddaa]]. By the [[Imperial Era|reign]] of the [[Galactic Empire]], it had gained a reputation as one of the roughest bars in [[the galaxy]]. During the early days of the Imperial Era, the [[Latero]] [[pilot]] [[Greez Dritus]] and former [[Jedi Knight]] [[Cere Junda]] entered into an altercation with [[smuggler]]s at the Slag Pit and were subsequently thrown out of the establishment. The two bonded over the incident and shared a drink of [[lum]] in a nearby alley.<ref name="JFO" />

{{Gamemechanics|canon=1|Star Wars Jedi: Fallen Order}}
In [[14 BBY]],<ref name="JFODate">''[[Star Wars: Timelines]]'' dates the events of ''[[Star Wars Jedi: Fallen Order]]'' to [[14 BBY]].</ref> Junda and Greez formed a [[Stinger Mantis crew|crew]] with the [[Jedi]] [[Padawan]] [[Cal Kestis]] aboard the ''[[Stinger Mantis]]'' [[luxury yacht]]. Dritus recounted the event and cited it as the first time he had clicked with Junda. In the same conversation, Junda recounted her own memories of the event, citing it as one of the best nights of her life that she'd had in years.<ref name="JFO" />
{{Endgame}}

In [[3 ABY]],<ref name="OutlawsDate">{{OutlawsDate}}</ref> the [[gambler]] [[Zana Gatta]] visited the Slag Pit a few days before visiting the [[casino]] [[cruiser]] [[Morenia]].<ref name="Outlaws">''[[Star Wars Outlaws]]''</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
The Slag Pit was [[canon]]ically mentioned in the [[2019]] video game ''[[Star Wars Jedi: Fallen Order]]'' during a conversation that may occur during travel between planets.<ref name="JFO" /> The Pit originates from the [[1994]] [[Star Wars Legends|Legends]] [[Star Wars comic books|comic book series]] [[Star Wars: Dark Empire II|''Dark Empire II'']].<ref name="Dark Empire II">''[[Star Wars: Dark Empire II]]''</ref>

